OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FJapan courts again say     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fsame-sex marriage ban is   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fillegal                    
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Two more rulings in Japanese district  
OL,6, courts have added weight to the push   
OL,7, for same-sex marriage to be legalised. 
OL,9,FThis week, courts in Tokyo and Sapporo 
OL,10,Fruled the nation's current ban was     
OL,11,F"unconstitutional", in line with       
OL,12,Fprevious landmark verdicts.            
OL,14,FThe rulings in separate cases found    
OL,15,Fthat the ban breached citizens' rights.
OL,17,FEven as they welcomed the verdicts,    
OL,18,Factivists warned that the historic step
OL,19,Fof legalising same-sex unions would    
OL,20,Fstill need to come from lawmakers.     
